" Configure navigation.
nnoremap j 3j
nnoremap k 3k

" Configure fast starting bookmarks.
nm S :bmarks! -tags=start<cr> " Open but keep current tab.
nm s SgTd " Open in current tab.

" Configure reading bookmarks.
nm a :bmark -tags=reading<cr> " Add a reading bookmark.
nm e :bmarks -tags=reading<cr>; " Display reading bookmarks.

" Configure once-a-day bookmarks.
nm x :bmarks! -tags=once<cr> " Open but keep current tab.
nm X :bmark -tags=once<cr> " Add a once-a-day bookmark.
